{"ja456:0.1":"Jataka ","ja456:0.2":"Ekadasakanipata ","ja456:0.3":"Matuposakavagga ","ja456:0.4":"2. Junhajataka ","ja456:1.1":"“Sunohi mayham vacanam janinda, ","ja456:1.2":"Atthena junhamhi idhanupatto; ","ja456:1.3":"Na brahmane addhike titthamane, ","ja456:1.4":"Gantabbamahu dvipadindasettha”. ","ja456:2.1":"“Sunomi titthami vadehi brahme, ","ja456:2.2":"Yenasi atthena idhanupatto; ","ja456:2.3":"Kam va tvamattham mayi patthayano, ","ja456:2.4":"Idhagama brahme tadingha bruhi”. ","ja456:3.1":"“Dadahi me gamavarani panca, ","ja456:3.2":"Dasisatam satta gavamsatani; ","ja456:3.3":"Parosahassanca suvannanikkhe, ","ja456:3.4":"Bhariya ca me sadisi dve dadahi. ","ja456:4.1":"Tapo nu te brahmana bhimsarupo, ","ja456:4.2":"Manta nu te brahmana cittarupa; ","ja456:4.3":"Yakkha nu te assava santi keci, ","ja456:4.4":"Attham va me abhijanasi kattam. ","ja456:5.1":"Na me tapo atthi na capi manta, ","ja456:5.2":"Yakkhapi me assava natthi keci; ","ja456:5.3":"Atthampi te nabhijanami kattam, ","ja456:5.4":"Pubbe ca kho sangatimattamasi. ","ja456:6.1":"Pathamam idam dassanam janato me, ","ja456:6.2":"Na tabhijanami ito purattha; ","ja456:6.3":"Akkhahi me pucchito etamattham, ","ja456:6.4":"Kada kuhim va ahu sangamo no. ","ja456:7.1":"Gandhararajassa puramhi ramme, ","ja456:7.2":"Avasimhase takkasilayam deva; ","ja456:7.3":"Tatthandhakaramhi timisikayam, ","ja456:7.4":"Amsena amsam samaghattayimha. ","ja456:8.1":"Te tattha thatvana ubho janinda, ","ja456:8.2":"Saraniyam vitisarayimha tattha; ","ja456:8.3":"Sayeva no sangatimattamasi, ","ja456:8.4":"Tato na paccha na pure ahosi. ","ja456:9.1":"Yada kadaci manujesu brahme, ","ja456:9.2":"Samagamo sappurisena hoti; ","ja456:9.3":"Na pandita sangatisanthavani, ","ja456:9.4":"Pubbe katam vapi vinasayanti. ","ja456:10.1":"Balava kho sangatisanthavani, ","ja456:10.2":"Pubbe katam vapi vinasayanti; ","ja456:10.3":"Bahumpi balesu katam vinassati, ","ja456:10.4":"Tatha hi bala akatannurupa. ","ja456:11.1":"Dhira ca kho sangatisanthavani, ","ja456:11.2":"Pubbe katam vapi na nasayanti; ","ja456:11.3":"Appampi dhiresu katam na nassati, ","ja456:11.4":"Tatha hi dhira sukatannurupa. ","ja456:12.1":"Dadami te gamavarani panca, ","ja456:12.2":"Dasisatam satta gavamsatani; ","ja456:12.3":"Parosahassanca suvannanikkhe, ","ja456:12.4":"Bhariya ca te sadisi dve dadami. ","ja456:13.1":"Evam satam hoti samecca raja, ","ja456:13.2":"Nakkhattarajariva tarakanam; ","ja456:13.3":"Apurati kasipati tathaham, ","ja456:13.4":"Tayapi me sangamo ajja laddho”ti. ","ja456:14.1":"Junhajatakam dutiyam. "}